name: Black Strawberry Cake
overview: Trap Runner Bonus Worlds This one is dedicated to all Amiga users who had fun in playing our game Trap Runner. Special features: New introduction story. Two brand new worlds, spanning 4 classical jump'n run levels, 1 jetpack level and 1 final bossfight each world. 10 new songs plus some short jingles. Two new game elements: Pushing boxes and jumping on a trampoline. New Outro. Hope you've a lot of fun playing the Bonus worlds!
